2006-07-19  Shahzad Muzaffar <Shahzad.Muzaffar@cern.ch>

	* src/IgConfigElement.cc: Bug fixed for the loacl unix accounts
	by making sure that ~/.iguana directory is writable and executable.

2006-07-05  Shahzad Muzaffar <Shahzad.Muzaffar@cern.ch>

	* interface/IgConfigElement.h, src/IgConfigElement.cc: Re-design
	interface and now make use of template to get/put value/values,
	Now by default it reads the ~/.iguana/iguana.conf file if not provided
	via --ig-config commnad-line argument, functionality to save the
	configuration in a file also available now.
	* test/test_IgConfigElement.cpp: Updated for new interface and added new
	tests.

2006-06-23  Shahzad Muzaffar <Shahzad.Muzaffar@cern.ch>

	* src/plugin.cc: Newly added file for Igconfig plugin(actually added
	now).

2006-06-23  Shahzad Muzaffar <Shahzad.Muzaffar@cern.ch>

	* src/plugin.cc: Newly added file for Igconfig plugin.
	* BuildFile: Define IgConfig as a seal plugin.
	* interface/IgConfigElement.h, src/IgConfigElement.cc: Renamed member
	function get to getValue, new functionality to replace ${key} with
	the value of key already defined in the config file or from the
	environment variable, functionality added to provide a prefix to be
	added for subsequent getValue calls e.g. if one wants to get values
	of /Iguana/Setup/Session, /Iguana/Setup/Caption, /Iguana/Setup/Size/X,
	/Iguana/Setup/Size/Y then one way to do this to set the prefix to
	/Iguana/Setup and then call getValue with key as Session, Caption, 
	Size/X or Size/Y.

2006-06-12  Shahzad Muzaffar <Shahzad.Muzaffar@cern.ch>

	* src/IgConfigElement.cc: Fixed the retrieval of bool type.
	* test/test_IgConfigElement.cpp: Verbose out and added some more tests.

2006-06-12  Shahzad Muzaffar <Shahzad.Muzaffar@cern.ch>

	* interface/IgConfigElement.h, src/IgConfigElement.cc: Support for
	boolean values added.
	* test/Buildfile, test/test_IgConfigElement.cpp: Test added to check the
	functionality of the IgConfigElement.

2006-06-09  Shahzad Muzaffar <Shahzad.Muzaffar@cern.ch>

	* interface/config.h: Newly added config file for IgConfig package.
	* interface/IgConfigElement.h, src/IgConfigElement.cc: First
